Everything we make
is in Colorado right now.

00:04:03,510 --> 00:04:04,611
Greiner:
So, two questions.

00:04:04,611 --> 00:04:06,680
Taylor: Okay.
One ‐‐
what does it weigh?

00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:11,852
75 pounds on the large box,
55 on the small box.

00:04:11,852 --> 00:04:12,486
Okay.

00:04:12,486 --> 00:04:14,554
And then we have
new products coming where,

00:04:14,554 --> 00:04:16,556
when they're in plastic,
they're gonna be much lighter.

00:04:16,556 --> 00:04:19,292
