any outside capital?

00:04:40,914 --> 00:04:41,481
No.

00:04:41,481 --> 00:04:43,416
So, what we did ‐‐
we took our savings.

00:04:43,416 --> 00:04:46,586
I got $250,000 invested
in this entire process.

00:04:46,586 --> 00:04:48,355
