to what price point?

00:05:26,359 --> 00:05:28,295
Well, yeah, our cost on that
is around $748.

00:05:28,295 --> 00:05:30,564
We can bring that down
in the $300, $200 range.

00:05:30,564 --> 00:05:33,400
