I'm sure.

00:05:39,673 --> 00:05:42,142
But, you know, being in
Colorado's not a bad thing,

00:05:42,142 --> 00:05:43,243
but first,
let me say this ‐‐

00:05:43,243 --> 00:05:44,411
you know,
there's an old saying ‐‐

00:05:44,411 --> 00:05:46,179
