the beginning stages.

00:06:27,554 --> 00:06:31,124
And so, for those reasons,
I'm out.

00:06:31,124 --> 00:06:34,361
♪♪

00:06:34,361 --> 00:06:38,498
In the last six months,
we've tripled our sales.

00:06:38,498 --> 00:06:40,433
We haven't even
gotten out there yet.

00:06:40,433 --> 00:06:42,402
O'Leary: You know,
